        <p class="c1"><span class="c5"></span></p>
        <p class="c7"><span class="c14">Customer</span></p>
        <p class="c1"><span class="c3"></span></p>
        <p class="c1"><span class="c3"></span></p>
        <p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">Select</span></p>
        <p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p>
        <ul class="c9 lst-kix_3o4uitwv8bu-0 start">
          <li class="c0 li-bullet-0">
            <span class="c4">
              Shows the customers names stored inside the database, with update and delete buttons.
            </span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p>
        <p class="c2 c7"><span class="c6">Select AJAX</span></p>
        <p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p>
        <ul class="c9 lst-kix_3o4uitwv8bu-0">
          <li class="c0 li-bullet-0">
            <span class="c4">Search the customers name inserted by the admin, with update and delete buttons. It&rsquo;s not necessary to reload the page thanks to AJAX.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">Insert</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_10d4ayis06qk-0 start"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c3">Let the customer( or admin ) add a new customer, it also is the register.</span></li></ul><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">Update</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_bbwszwyli7da-0 start"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c3">Let the customer( or admin ) modify a customer, it also is the settings for the user.</span></li></ul><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">Delete</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_csdkqevu2dh8-0 start"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c12 c4">Delete</span><span class="c3">: it doesn&#39;t actually delete the customer, but it changes the status from 1 to 0.</span></li><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c3">Let the customer delete his own account.</span></li><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c3">Let the admin delete the customer in the database.</span></li></ul><p class="c1"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c1"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7"><span class="c5">Room</span></p><p class="c1"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c1"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">Check Availability</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_3o4uitwv8bu-0"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c4">Let the customer( or admin ) insert two dates, and show the rooms that are available during that period. It also shows a button that makes an automatic reservation of that room.</span></li></ul><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">Select</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_3o4uitwv8bu-0"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c4">Shows the rooms stored inside the database, with update, delete buttons, and an image of the room.</span></li></ul><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">Insert</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c6"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_10d4ayis06qk-0"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c4">Let the admin add a new room.</span></li></ul><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">Update</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_bbwszwyli7da-0"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c4">Let the admin modify a room.</span></li></ul><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">Delete</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_bbwszwyli7da-0"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c4">Let the admin delete a room, it &nbsp;</span><span class="c12 c4">permanently deletes</span><span class="c3">&nbsp;the room.</span></li></ul><p class="c1"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c1"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7"><span class="c5">Room Type</span></p><p class="c1"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c1"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">Select</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_3o4uitwv8bu-0"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c4">Shows the room types stored inside the database, with update, delete buttons.</span></li></ul><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">Insert</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c6"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_10d4ayis06qk-0"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c4">Let the admin add a new room type.</span></li></ul><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">Update</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_bbwszwyli7da-0"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c4">Let the admin modify a room type.</span></li></ul><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">Delete</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_bbwszwyli7da-0"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c4">Let the admin delete a room type, it &nbsp;</span><span class="c12 c4">permanently deletes</span><span class="c4">&nbsp;the room.</span></li></ul><p class="c1"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c1"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7"><span class="c5">Reservation</span></p><p class="c1"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c1"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">My Reservations</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_3o4uitwv8bu-0"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c4">Shows the reservations made by the logged user( admin, or customer ), if the reservation is in the booked status the user can change the dates or cancel the reservation, if the reservation status is &ldquo;check out&rdquo; the customer will be capable of leaving one comment( and just one ).</span></li></ul><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">Select</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_3o4uitwv8bu-0"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c4">Shows the reservations stored inside the database, with update, delete buttons.</span></li></ul><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">Insert</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c6"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_10d4ayis06qk-0"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c4">Let the admin add a new reservation, without checking dates.</span></li></ul><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">Update</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_bbwszwyli7da-0"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c4">Let the admin modify a reservation.</span></li></ul><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">Delete</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_bbwszwyli7da-0"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c3">Let the admin move a reservation from the table &ldquo;reservations&rdquo; to the table &ldquo;records&rdquo; to maintain clean the &ldquo;reservations&rdquo; table, the &ldquo;reservation status&rdquo; mustn&#39;t be booked.</span></li></ul><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c11">Cancel</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_bbwszwyli7da-0"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c3">Let the customer( or admin ) change the reservation status to cancel.</span></li></ul><p class="c1"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c1"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7"><span class="c5">Comments</span></p><p class="c1"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c1"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">Select</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_3o4uitwv8bu-0"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c4">Shows the comments made in the reservations stored inside the database.</span></li></ul><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2"><span class="c6">Insert</span></p><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><ul class="c9 lst-kix_3o4uitwv8bu-0"><li class="c0 li-bullet-0"><span class="c4">Let the customer( or admin ) insert a comment to a reservation, </span><span class="c4 c12">it can only be one comment per reservation</span><span class="c3">.</span></li></ul><p class="c1 c2"><span class="c3"></span></p><p class="c7 c2">
        <span class="c6">Update</span></p>
        <p class="c1 c2">
          <span class="c3"></span>
        </p>
    <ul class="c9 lst-kix_3o4uitwv8bu-0">
      <li class="c0 li-bullet-0">
        <span class="c4">Let the admin change the status of the comment( published, hidden, banned ).</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
